  org.sakaiproject.sms.hibernate.bean.SearchResultContainer<T>

public class SearchResultContainer<T extends BaseModel>
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used my the criteria search methods. It is used to house the page result set that will be returned to the UI as well as other attributes that will be used.
